PrecisAmendments to the CANADIAN INTERNATIONAL TRADE TRIBUNAL PROCUREMENT INQUIRY REGULATIONS which implement Canada's obligations arising from the coming into force of the WTO Agreement on Government Procurement and expand the jurisdiction of the CITT to include bid challenge complaints made by potential suppliers originating from countries that are signatories to the WTO Agreement of Government Procurement.

precis:
Amendments to the CANADIAN INTERNATIONAL TRADE TRIBUNAL PROCUREMENT INQUIRY
REGULATIONS which implement Canada's obligations arising from the coming
into force of the WTO Agreement on Government Procurement and expand the
jurisdiction of the CITT to include bid challenge complaints made by
potential suppliers originating from countries that are signatories to the
WTO Agreement of Government Procurement.
